};
---

<ProjectPage {...projectData}>
  <p slot="description-first-paragraph">
    The DANA Project is a logistics center for the reception, organization, and distribution of donations for emergency situations, natural disasters, and humanitarian crises. This space allows us to respond quickly and efficiently to unexpected events, ensuring that aid reaches those who need it most.
  </p>
  
  <p slot="description-second-paragraph">
    Within the framework of this project, we implement a circular economy system to minimize waste and make the most of donations, thus contributing to environmental sustainability while fulfilling our humanitarian mission.
  </p>
</ProjectPage>

